### CREAR PRODUCTO
POST http://localhost:3000/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "producto a eliminar",
    "description": "eliminarrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrr",
    "price": 11111,
    "stock": 5,
    "imageUrl": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dzxa0ykpd/image/upload/v1780970041/D_716149-MLA82553365374_032025-C_wqdwiv.jpg"
}


### ACTUALIZAR PRODUCTO
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/products/6a281fae290edf788c0e772a
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "price": 8500
}


### OBTENER UN PRODUCTO
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products/6a281fae290edf788c0e772a


### ELIMINAR UN PRODUCTO
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/products/6a28417b4895e722fb433574


