### ADD TO CART
POST http://localhost:3000/api/cart/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userId": "6a1eff5638fab48282df7bee",
    "productId": "6a281fae290edf788c0e772a",
    "quantity": 1
}

### GET CART
GET http://localhost:3000/api/cart/get/6a1eff5638fab48282df7bee

### UPTADE CART
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/cart/update/6a1eff5638fab48282df7bee
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userId": "6a1eff5638fab48282df7bee",
    "productId": "6a281fae290edf788c0e772a",
    "quantity": 10
}

### DELETE CART
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/cart/delete/6a1eff5638fab48282df7bee

